Interface NestedSQLValue<T,N>

  • Type Parameters:

    N - type of nested SQLValue
    All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface NestedSQLValue<T,N>
extends SQLValue<T>, GroupingSQLValue<T>
    A SQLValue that wraps a different one It includes default methods to handle any nested GroupingSQLValue.
